          DIRECTIVE      CATEGORY

          DB             1
          DS             1
          DW             1
          ELSE           4
          END            1
          ENDIF          4
          ENDM           3
          EQU            1
          FORMLN         2
          IF             4
          LIST           2
          MACRO          3
          NLIST          2
          ORG            1
          PAGE           2
          SET            1
